  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "# Feature Issue\n\nCurrently the only way to find your chat key is the tiny icon in the top right corner of `Profile` view.\nSeveral users have complained that they were unable to find their own chat key and share it.\n\n### User Story\n\nAs a user, I want to to be able to actually find my chat key.\n\n### Description\n\nThe icon is too hidden, too small, and - as one user in `#support` suggested - looks like a logout button. What we need is a more obvious way - or ways - to get and share your chat key/ENS name.",
