    "body": "[9 designs later](https://www.figma.com/file/TNCyHKtR3sx5EL6YznFWUa4O/Profile?node-id=4323%3A19953), here's what I propose to do\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1526\" alt=\"Screenshot 2020-02-26 at 09 38 09\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/75327174-39f88a00-587c-11ea-83de-e76901451642.png\">\r\n\r\n1. Add the chat key below your currently used username.\r\n2. Embed the avatar, name and key into touchable so tapping any one of them will bring up the share popover\r\n3. Use platform specific share icons, since for Android users, the upward arrow is mostly unfamiliar.\r\n\r\nDesign can be found [here](https://www.figma.com/file/TNCyHKtR3sx5EL6YznFWUa4O/Profile?node-id=4336%3A1208)  ",
